msgctxt "Npc_DungeonPriest_HeroGerudoRelief_001"
msgid ""
"I applaud your courage in coming here.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"The locations that will be revealed to\n"
"you are of trials that will enhance\n"
"the power sleeping within.\n"
"Do not let your guard down..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGerudoRelief_000"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hm? <2.pa>How strange to see someone else\n"
"at this ample altitude. I wonder what\n"
"brought him here..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGerudoRelief_002"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh! How embarrassing. I'm afraid\n"
"traveling on my own encourages\n"
"me to talk to myself on occasion."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGerudoRelief_004"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah, such a rush of happiness I feel at\n"
"being able to sing while the <2.se_co>Divine\n"
"Beast<3.re_co> watches over us..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: auto_advance
#. 2: sound
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: set_colour (blue)
#. 6: reset_colour
#. 7: auto_advance
msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGerudoRelief_005"
msgid ""
"<1.au_ad><2.so>The song my teacher left behind...\n"
"There's <3.se_co>a verse<4.re_co> about the trials that\n"
"<5.se_co>Champion Urbosa <6.re_co>overcame.\n"
"<7.au_ad>Allow me to sing it for you..."
msgstr ""

